User Stories

As a visitor, I want to see other user's posts.
As a visitor, I want to click on a post to see more details.
As a visitor, I want to sign up for a free account. 
As a user, I want to post with a title, image, description.
As a user, I want to edit my post.
As a user, I want to delete a post that I wrote.
As a user, I want to like/unlike posts.

Business Rules

Posts are stored in a database. Images are stored on AWS S3.
A post consists of an image, a title, and description.
Posting an item automatically adds it to your account page and the wall all users can see.
Passwords must be encrypted.